data.description: Welcome to this big and spacious 5 bedroom 1 bath country style farm house with outbuildings located on just under 3 acres of land. This property boasts high ceilings, a spacious eat in kitchen with stainless steel appliances, oak hardwood floors under the carpet on first floor and second level, pocket doors, first floor laundry and a first floor bedroom currently used as an office. This property has a fenced in area for the owners dog and an above ground swimming pool. 1 car attached garage. This property is very unique and it will not last long. Make an appointment today!
